Linda McLean was a teacher at Pine Eagle Charter School in Halfway, Oregon in 2013 when a masked man burst in with a gun and told her 'You're dead' The 'active shooter' drill was a 'harebrained scheme' to test her 'preparedness' McLean is now suing the school district for post-traumatic stress disorder . 
  She was in her classroom during the drill and thought she was going to die . 
  She is suing administrators and the school board for 'punitive damages and attorney fees'